Unstrong: Space Calamity | Gameplay Demo (PC)
SUPPORT THE CHANNEL! SUBSCRIBE!

Sure, the world exploded and you're just drifting through space now, but you WILL find a way to make your planet whole again. Nothing can stop mad scientist ladies like Glasses! Soar through space and explore planets, moons and asteroids in this action-packed 3d platformer.
